ription\": \"Graph parsing, serialization, canonical byte generation, hashing, and RdfDelta transitions must be deterministic.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r4_knowledge_hook\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"description\": \"Turtle-based hook packs must load dynamically as graph laws and schedule deterministically.\",\n-        \"title\": \"Knowledge Hook Runtime & Deterministic Scheduling\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r5_ocel_prov\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"OCEL/PROV Evidence Projection & Replayable Receipts\",\n-        \"description\": \"Every graph transition must produce a replayable cryptographic receipt bundle and project PROV-O/OCEL.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r6_compliance\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"description\": \"Must pass structural analyses checking for forbidden execution surfaces and zero placeholder/stub/mock/fake-success patterns.\",\n-        \"title\": \"Compliance Checks & Anti-Fake Gates\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r7_ocel_self_audit\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"OCEL v2 Self-Audit Log Emission\",\n-        \"description\": \"Implement self-audit log generator emitting vision2030.self_audit.ocel.json.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r8_coverage_matrix\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"description\": \"Implement coverage mapping in coverage.rs and verify via scripts.\",\n-        \"title\": \"Coverage Matrix & Verification Scripts\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r9_proof_report\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"Vision 2030 Durable Proof Report\",\n-        \"description\": \"Establish Vision 2030 durable 