audit logs must project deterministically to and from RDF triple graphs.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Deterministic Graph Mapping\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_ard_mapping\",\n+      \"type\": \"ARDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"The substrate must be implemented as a single standalone Rust package at crates/ggen-graph with no feature flags.\",\n+        \"title\": \"One-Crate Package Boundary and No Feature Flags\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r1_one_crate\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Vocabulary constants must be emitted directly from public ontology profiles.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Public Ontology Governance and Vocabulary Emission\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r2_ontology\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Graph parsing, serialization, canonical byte generation, hashing, and RdfDelta transitions must be deterministic.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Deterministic Graph Substrate and Delta Conservation\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r3_deterministic\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Turtle-based hook packs must load dynamically as graph laws and schedule deterministically.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Knowledge Hook Runtime & Deterministic Scheduling\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r4_knowledge_hook\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Every graph transition must produce a replayable cryptographic receipt bundle and project PROV-O/OCEL.\",\n+        \"title\": \"OCEL/PROV Evidence Projection & Replayable Receipts\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r5_ocel_prov\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Must pass structural analyses checking for forbidden execution surfaces and zero placeholder/stub/mock/fake-success patterns.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Compliance Checks & Anti-Fake Gates\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r6_compliance\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Implement self-audit log generator emitting vision2030.self_audit.ocel.json.\",\n+        \"title\": \"OCEL v2 Self-Audit Log Emission\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r7_ocel_self_audit\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Implement coverage mapping in coverage.rs and verify via scripts.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Coverage Matrix & Verification Scripts\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r8_coverage_matrix\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Establish Vision 2030 durable proof report.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Vision 2030 Durable Proof Report\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r9_proof_report\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Ensure interchangeable parts where Genesis is the embedded core and ggen forms the outer membrane, adapter layer, and projection layer.\",\n+        \"title\": \"Genesis-bearing Interchangeable Part Architecture\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"req_r10_interchangeable\",\n+      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"milestone\": \"self_audit_verification\",\n+        \"target_date\": \"2026-05-26Z\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_cp_verify\",\n+      \"type\": \"GALLCheckpoint\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"namespace\": \"http://www.ocel-standard.org/ns#\",\n+        \"prefix\": \"ocel\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_public_ontology\",\n+      \"type\": \"PublicOntology\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"name\": \"Event\",\n+        \"uri\": \"http://www.ocel-standard.org/ns#Event\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_ontology_term_event\",\n+      \"type\": \"OntologyTerm\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"language\": \"rust\",\n+        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/src/ocel/self_audit.rs\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_source_file_self_audit\",\n+      \"type\": \"SourceFile\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"framework\": \"cargo test\",\n+        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/tests/ocel_self_audit.rs\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_test_file_self_audit\",\n+      \"type\": \"TestFile\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"description\": \"Demonstrates generation and projection of self-audit log\",\n+        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/examples/self_audit_demo.rs\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_example_file_self_audit\",\n+      \"type\": \"ExampleFile\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"format\": \"json\",\n+        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/tests/fixtures/self_audit_log.json\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_fixture_file_self_audit\",\n+      \"type\": \"FixtureFile\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"interpreter\": \"bash\",\n+        \"path\": \"scripts/gall/external/09_verify_ocel_self_audit.sh\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_script_file_verify\",\n+      \"type\": \"ScriptFile\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"args\": \"test --package ggen-graph\",\n+        \"binary\": \"cargo\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_command_test\",\n+      \"type\": \"Command\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"execution_host\": \"localhost\",\n+        \"exit_code\": \"0\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_command_run_1\",\n+      \"type\": \"CommandRun\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"sha256\": \"9f86d081884c7d659a2feaa0c55ad015a3bf4f1b2b0b822cd15d6c15b0f00a08\",\n+        \"size_bytes\": \"1024\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_evidence_artifact_1\",\n+      \"type\": \"EvidenceArtifact\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"block_index\": \"42\",\n+        \"hash\": \"eb3a28b0f4e1f72da89f2cf0f95b9d3bb8cf03ffdcf82309e7116744f2ef08eb\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_graph_receipt_1\",\n+      \"type\": \"GraphReceipt\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"branch_coverage\": \"0.921\",\n+        \"line_coverage\": \"0.965\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_coverage_matrix_1\",\n+      \"type\": \"CoverageMatrix\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"approver\": \"OrchestratorAgent\",\n+        \"status\": \"Promoted\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_promotion_decision_1\",\n+      \"type\": \"PromotionDecision\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"attributes\": {\n+        \"name\": \"RealtimeMultiAgentConsensus\",\n+        \"reason\": \"Out of scope for deterministic local execution model\"\n+      },\n+      \"id\": \"obj_unsupported_capability_1\",\n+      \"type\": \"UnsupportedCapability\"\n     }\n   ]\n }\n\\ No newline at end of file\n" .

